'''Dransagalor''' was a [[black dragon]]. An acquaintance of [[Sammaster]], the two of them met, alongside [[Cylla Morieth]], in [[Uktar 9]] of the {{yearlinkName|1372}}. Caught in the early stages of a [[Rage of Dragons]], he attacked Sammaster together with [[Ormalagos]]; after he calmed their frenzy, Sammaster warned them a frenzy without end was coming and offered them the transformation into a [[dracolich]]. Though Needle was skeptical, Dransagalor had portents in his dreams that the frenzy would be truly without end, and was thusly resigned to his fate as a dracolich.{{cite book/The Rage||14}}

He could cast the most elementary dismissal spell for most magical effects, likely [[dispel magic]].
